       "itertools.accumulate.__bases__.__len__() == 1 — accumulate is a C extension type defined in Modules/itertoolsmodule.c; it inherits directly from object and has exactly one base class; tuple.__len__() returns 1; no prior itertools spec checks accumulate.__bases__.__len__() via itrtoolsextra81; new to extra81"]
    - [accumulate_bases_0_name_eq_object,
