       ["object"],
       true,
       "itertools.accumulate.__bases__[0].__name__.__eq__('object') == True — accumulate is a C extension type that inherits directly from object; its only base class is object whose __name__ is 'object' (6 chars); str.__eq__('object') returns True; no prior itertools spec checks accumulate.__bases__[0].__name__ via itrtoolsextra81; new to extra81"]

